When PBFX enters the liquidation state, the customer's isolated funds cannot be used to compensate PBFX creditors or banks. We ensure maximum security for your fund safety and assure that there is no mishandling of funds. Our priority is transparency funding process with our clients and that helps us build a trustworthy relationship.



PBFX aims to provide traders with comprehensive technical support and a complete information interpretation and analysis system in customer support. So that traders have a deeper understanding of trading!



In order to provide better service for customers in different countries, PBFX will add language support from time to time according to traders‚Äô data in different countries. Currently, customers can get the following 3 languages: English, Chinese, and Malay.



PBFX delivers professional financial knowledge training through the strict points assessment system for our employees, account managers, and broker to provide complete business consulting services to traders as we are willing to provide comprehensive and professional support.



We provide free customer service including WhatsApp, Telegram, Facebook, Instagram, Skype, Weibo, and WeChat online customer service systems. We handle clients' transactions and queries as soon as possible once we received messages, calls, or emails from clients.
